long_description:
Inputs
------
default : Vector
    The input vector that will be the x axis of OrderedPair.
y : Vector
    The input vector that will be the y axis of OrderedPair.
short_description: The VECTOR_2_ORDERED_PAIR node returns the OrderedPair where x and y axes are the input nodes.

returns.description: The OrderedPair that is generated from the input vectors
